{"type": "article", "id": 24165, "title": "手电筒式的灯", "description": "", "date": "2016-03-21T07:00:19Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 161922, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 29, "image": "img/article/article_show/20160702140304q78WoTZyrjVU0lwp.jpeg", "contents": "\n\n<p class=\"\">这盏的灯的设计源于万花筒，通过移动外面的圆环来改变光线的强弱。灯柱有 5 种不同的颜色，即便是完全遮住光源，也能照射出灯柱的颜色，有些游戏的趣味。它是由 ABS 塑料和铝材料制作，安装电池使用，有点像手电筒。售价 45 美元，<a href=\"http://www.ckie.com/products/kaleido-torch-night-light#.Vu6pJMdhyS-\">这里是购买链接。</a><br></p>\n<div class=\"com-insert-images medium-insert-active medium-insert-images-wide\">\n<figure class=\"\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140301EDxp7A8uqzvewnc0.jpg\" alt=\"\" class=\"medium-insert-image-active\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n<figcaption class=\"medium-insert-caption-placeholder\"></figcaption></figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140302GTj6NbJsw0HdDKFl.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140302nByPtl4FmbMxNp5e.gif\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.53904762\" data-format=\"gif\">\r\n</figure><figure style=\"margin:0;\">\r\n    <img src=\"img/uploads/20160702140303Mc2hobmfOdwpYsvq.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-ratio=\"0.76095238\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n</figure>\n</div>\n\n\n"}